This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with end-to-end speech translation, which is a subfield of natural language processing. The paper also proposes a knowledge distillation approach to improve the performance of the ST model, which involves transferring knowledge from a text translation model. This approach involves the use of machine learning techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SD (Sound), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
